    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754740/extras/90390de01f12ba89d9f3ec3b2aef9e9f.avif?t=1706275216\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><br>每次这对父子兴高采烈地出去冒险，但最后都以麻烦收场。但这并没有阻止他们要去山间散散步！在平和的大自然中能出什么差错呢？但随即这位父亲就从山上滚了下去。还好他没什么事，但他一直滚到了山脚下，而他儿子还在山顶上呢！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754740/extras/b485005cf88f7cd8e2b6d4482beb1519.poster.avif?t=1706275216\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754740/extras/b485005cf88f7cd8e2b6d4482beb1519.webm?t=1706275216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754740/extras/b485005cf88f7cd8e2b6d4482beb1519.mp4?t=1706275216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>帮这位笨拙但父爱满满的父亲尽快找到他儿子。打通由五颜六色的石块组成的关卡即可不断向上攀爬。将3个或以上的相同石块组合起来就能消除前进道路上的障碍，最终征服这座高山。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754740/extras/fe95e2a06c66d87302ac4dcd08ff59cf.poster.avif?t=1706275216\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754740/extras/fe95e2a06c66d87302ac4dcd08ff59cf.webm?t=1706275216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754740/extras/fe95e2a06c66d87302ac4dcd08ff59cf.mp4?t=1706275216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你可以完成所有关卡目标并在每个关卡都获得三颗星吗？使用不同种类的增强道具可助你轻松通关。小男孩孤独地在山顶上等待，所以别让他等太久哦。在享受轻松惬意的游戏氛围的同时，尽快让父子俩团聚吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754740/extras/3495113f10d573467b83477b4addabee.avif?t=1706275216\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>充满挑战的100个关卡<br></li><li>帮助父亲攀上山顶<br></li><li>让父子重聚<br></li><li>清除所有障碍<br></li><li>使用各种增强道具<br></li><li>将3个或以上的相同石块组合<br></li><li>漂亮的手绘画面<br></li><li>气氛轻松</li></ul>",
